1. Entitlements:
    a. Get all roles:
        GET: /incdocs/entitlement/roles
        RESULT:
            [
                {
                    "roleID": 1,
                    "roleName": "ADMIN",
                    "description": "Administrator"
                },
                {
                    "roleID": 2,
                    "roleName": "GROUP_HEAD",
                    "description": "Group Head managing the portfolio"
                }..
            ]

    b. Get role by id:
        GET: /incdocs/entitlement/role?id=1
        RESULT:
                    {
                        "roleID": 1,
                        "roleName": "ADMIN",
                        "description": "Administrator"
                    }
    c.